<function>

access:   public

name: setActive

param: bool, $flag

return: void

</function>

Makes the cache active (true) or inactive (false).

* Parameters:

 * bool //$flag//: True to turn on, false to turn off.

* Returns void

Makes the cache active (true) or inactive (false).

Example:

<code type="php">
$cache = Solar::factory('Solar_Cache');

// turn the cache off
$cache->setActive(false);

// turn it back on
$cache->setActive(true);
</code>